title: Trump Flops, Olivia Rodrigo WINNING 5.25.21

description:
In episode 916, Miles and guest host Joelle Monique are joined by comedian and Cold Brew Got Me Like host Chris Crofton to discuss Maxine Waters thoughts on qualified immunity, Trump's blog, the new Olivia Rodrigo album, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. WATCH: ‘I Want Qualified Immunity Out!’ Rep. Waters On George Floyd Justice in Policing Act
  2. Trump is sliding toward online irrelevance. His new blog isn’t helping.
  3. Olivia Rodrigo - SOUR
  4. LISTEN: My Girl (Nick Bike's Rocksteady Mix) (Version)
